    public abstract class GenericPatternMatch
extends BasePatternMatch
    Generic signature object implementation. Please instantiate using BaseMatcher.newMatch(Object...) or BaseMatcher.newEmptyMatch(). See also the generated matcher and signature of the pattern, with pattern-specific API simplifications.
